  "texts": [
    "Therefore, we need event type information to identify such trigger words.Most existing methods were unable to handle this situation satisfactorily.",
    "The interaction between event types and trigger words provides event type information, which greatly aids in identifying implicit trigger words.",
    "Some excellent methods based on QA or machine reading comprehension only provided a keyword as a query for the event type, for example, \"[EVENT]\".",
    "However, these methods failed to obtain event type information.",
    "Some promptbased methods designed different templates for each event type."
  ],
